X-94!

416
00:18:36,759 --> 00:18:39,938
<i>Doutor Palmer,
voz reconhecida</i>

417
00:18:41,097 --> 00:18:43,441
Sim.

418
00:18:49,371 --> 00:18:50,682
A festa acabou!

419
